
TY  - JOUR
T1  - Transparency and Percent Plans
AU  - Kapor, Adam
Y1  - 2025/11/01
PY  - 2025
DA  - 2025/11/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA18385
T2  - Econometrica
